    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s clean, runs great, and is just waiting for its next owner to enjoy. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
