      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a 2011 Porsche Cayman S (987.2), a masterclass in mid-engine dynamics. This specimen features the 3.4L flat-six equipped with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), effectively bypassing the IMS bearing issues of previous generations. Power is delivered through a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle, ensuring a direct mechanical connection. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a McPherson strut suspension geometry that offers exceptional turn-in precision and a low polar moment of inertia. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system refresh and a new set of high-performance ignition coils. The braking system retains its bite with four-piston monobloc calipers and ventilated rotors. This is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car for those who prioritize hydraulic steering feedback and linear power delivery over modern electronic interference.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. No major issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i finished in Sophisto Grey Metallic. This vehicle represents a superb balance of luxury and performance, currently in strong operational and aesthetic condition. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, with only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with careful road use. Inside, the Black Dakota leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, complemented by elegant Fineline Ridge wood trim. All technological features, including the iDrive 6.0 system, navigation, and Gesture Control, are fully functional and responsive. Under the hood, the 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline 6-cylinder engine runs smoothly, benefiting from a documented service history at authorized dealerships. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and the installation of a new set of Continental run-flat tires. This car has been consistently garage-kept and remains smoke-free, offering a premium driving experience for its next owner. Clean title and two sets of keys included.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
